<h1>Contact the College</h1>

<div class="contact-info">
    <h3>Location</h3>
    <p>
        College of Winterhold<br />
        Winterhold, Skyrim<br />
        (Northeast coast, along the Sea of Ghosts)
    </p>

    <h3>Send a Courier</h3>
    <p>
        Address letters to:<br />
        <em>Arcanaeum Library, College of Winterhold, Winterhold, Skyrim</em>
    </p>

    <h3>Magical Communication</h3>
    <p>
        For urgent magical matters, use the sending stone in the Hall of Elements.<br />
        <small>(Standard sending fee: 5 septims per message)</small>
    </p>

    <h3>Admissions Office</h3>
    <p>Speak with Faralda at the main gate for entrance exams and enrollment inquiries.</p>
</div>